    ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê -->
    <record id="view_youtube_download_player" model="ir.ui.view">
        <field name="name">youtube.download.player</field>
        <field name="model">youtube.download</field>
        <field name="arch" type="xml">
            <form string="üé¨ Lecteur Vid√©o" class="o_youtube_player_form" create="0" edit="0" delete="0">
                <sheet>
                    <field name="state" invisible="1"/>
                    <field name="file_path" invisible="1"/>
                    <field name="file_exists" invisible="1"/>
                    <field name="output_format" invisible="1"/>
                    <field name="quality" invisible="1"/>
                    <field name="video_thumbnail_url" invisible="1"/>
                    <field name="video_author" invisible="1"/>
                    <field name="video_duration" invisible="1"/>
                    <field name="video_duration_display" invisible="1"/>
                    <field name="file_size" invisible="1"/>
                    <field name="file_size_display" invisible="1"/>

                    <div class="yt_player_container">
                        <!-- Lecteur Vid√©o (tous formats vid√©o, y compris non-natifs transcod√©s √† la vol√©e) -->
                        <div class="yt_player_media_wrapper"
                             invisible="output_format in ('mp3', 'wav', 'ogg', 'flac', 'aac', 'm4a', 'wma', 'opus')">
                            <video class="yt_player_video"
                                   controls="controls"
                                   preload="metadata"
                                   autoplay="autoplay"
                                   playsinline="true"
                                   style="width: 100%; max-height: 70vh;">
                                Votre navigateur ne supporte pas la lecture vid√©o HTML5.
                            </video>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Lecteur Audio (tous formats audio) -->
                        <div invisible="output_format not in ('mp3', 'wav', 'ogg', 'flac', 'aac', 'm4a', 'wma', 'opus')">
                            <div class="yt_player_audio_visual">
                                <div class="yt_player_audio_placeholder">
                                    <span class="yt_player_audio_icon">üéµ</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <audio controls="controls" preload="metadata"
                                   autoplay="autoplay"
                                   style="width: 100%; margin-top: 16px;">
                                Votre navigateur ne supporte pas la lecture audio HTML5.
                            </audio>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Info vid√©o -->
